WorkItem.Description:
The dates in the attached xls are formated with 4-digits for the year. But when I read the file with phpExcel and use the CSV Writer I get only a 2-digit year in the CSV.

```
$inputFileType = PHPExcel_IOFactory::identify($file->getTempName());
$excelReader = PHPExcel_IOFactory::createReader($inputFileType);
$phpExcel = $excelReader->load($file->getTempName());
$csvWriter = new PHPExcel_Writer_CSV($phpExcel);
$csvWriter->setSheetIndex($phpExcel->getActiveSheetIndex());
$csvWriter->save("myCSV.csv");
```
